GENERAL THEATRES, Inc., a Corporation, et al., v. METRO-GOLDWYN-MAYER DISTRIBUTING CORPORATION, a Corporation, et al. No. 1210. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Aug. 17, 1936. Ewing, Arnold & Weinberger, of Denver,-Colo., for appellants. Thomas J. Morrissey, U. S. Atty., and Hodges, Wilson & Vidal, all of Denver, Colo., for appellees.

Before LEWIS and PHILLIPS, Circuit Judges.

PER CÜRIAM.

Appeal dismissed on stipulations.
